[Pelosi Trade](https://pelositrade.com) is a stock trading assistant that helps users get notified when congress members trade.

![](https://ph-files.imgix.net/ccffa841-ebdf-433b-9e70-fd79da9d983e.png?auto=compress&codec=mozjpeg&cs=strip&auto=format&fm=pjpg&w=1100&h=613&fit=max&dpr=2)

Ported a TTRPG (solo rpg) game that I found via itch.to: Sweaters By Hedgehog to discord as a bot using node.js and ngrok.
Added localizations in en, cn, fr, es, de and kr
Standardized logging
Redesigned and ported to AWS in Python
Streamlined deployment by using AWS CLI and Cloudformation

